title: Authorities find black box after a deadly Nepal crash
text:
Authorities find black box after a deadly Nepal crash 10:32am GMT - 01:23 
A black box has been pulled from the wreckage of a deadly plane crash in Nepal, which may provide clues as to what led to an air disaster that killed 49 people on Monday. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
